{"tid":836503,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟擺低失戀二三事","createTime":"2018-09-25T16:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T05:21:37.000Z","uid":120046,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"816651b689949e064bf9670230a317f61d2db916","tid":836503,"uid":120046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T16:38:50.000Z","msg":"記得失戀第二日要上體育堂<br />\n我打打下乒乓波啲眼淚係咁流<br />\n個體育阿sir見到 問我發生咩事<br />\n我諗呢個時候冇咩人會直說<br />\n我唯有答自己好唔舒服<br />\n個阿sir即刻好緊張咁話搵個missy送我去sick room<br />\n嗰陣時我真係忍唔住 係咁喊<br />\n為免自己喺度影響大家上堂 於是我點頭 就去左sick room<br />\n到落左堂 個阿sir即刻嚟左sick room搵我<br />\n問我ok嘛<br />\n嗰一刻 我見到眼前既人唔係男朋友<br />\n當頭棒喝 終於認清事實<br />\n係 我失戀了"},{"pid":"de3ab807e8be978bf3bcd2f6cd5b2ff185919412","tid":836503,"uid":150400,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T16:41:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b801c4515a9b46b222478ee5a33deba25a04292a","tid":836503,"uid":190749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T23:48:58.000Z","msg":"暗戀--&gt;暖昧--&gt;失戀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805d525a877ade750cbd679b8ced5ca2cd854078","tid":836503,"uid":74418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:21:37.000Z","msg":"好人卡"}]}